name: My Asian Nanny
description: This agency helps families in Ohio (including Cleveland and Columbus) hire trusted nannies, housekeepers, and offers Chinese Confinement services. They have been in operation for over 10 years and emphasize background-checked and vetted caregivers

name: Asian American Community Services (Healthy Asian Youth)
description: Healthy Asian Youth (HAY) provides after-school and summer programming for low-income youth in Central Ohio. They offer tutoring, recreation, mentorship, and life skills

name: Addresses:
description: ASIA serves, supports, and advocates for Asian Americans and Pacific Islanders, immigrants, and refugees in Northeast Ohio. Their Children, Youth, & Family Services department provides programming for youth development, acculturation, and academic support, including language-specific peer support groups and parenting education

name: GoInstaCare
description: This platform helps families find Chinese-speaking nannies for bilingual childcare in Columbus and other areas. They offer services for child care, senior care, and home care

name: Care.com (Ohio Chinese-Speaking Nanny)
description: Care.com lists various services, including Chinese-speaking nannies in Ohio. You can search for nannies in specific cities like Cincinnati, Columbus, and Dayton

name: Ohio Nanny Family Collective
description: A boutique nanny agency in Columbus, Ohio, that places nannies with families in Central and Northwest Ohio

name: Hunny Nanny Agency
description: This agency supports professional families in Cincinnati and Cleveland by helping them hire reliable and vetted nannies

name: AMERICA'S CHILDCARE LLC
description: This is a licensed child care center in Columbus, OH, offering various services including before and after school care. While not explicitly Chinese-American-owned, it is a licensed facility that may cater to diverse needs

name: ChildCareEd
description: This organization offers online training and courses for early childhood and child care professionals. While not a direct babysitting service, it supports professionals in the field
